{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"e4b2d9f1-5a62-4aaf-aeaf-b7ac5415cb79","content":"There's no existing file in the directory, so I'll show you the conversion directly.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd the `x:DataType` attribute to your `ContentPage` pointing to your ViewModel:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout>\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize, StringFormat='Font size: {0}'}\" />\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n**Key change:** `x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\"` tells the XAML compiler the expected type of `BindingContext`, so all `{Binding ...}` expressions are resolved at compile time.\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\n1. **Enable strict mode** in your `.csproj`:\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <MauiStrictXamlCompilation>true</MauiStrictXamlCompilation>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n   This promotes binding warnings to **errors**, failing the build if a property name is misspelled or doesn't exist on the declared `x:DataType`.\n\n2. **Without strict mode**, the compiler still emits warnings (e.g., `XC0045`) for unresolved bindings. Run:\n   ```\n   dotnet build -warnaserror:XC0045\n   ```\n   to treat them as errors in CI.\n\n3. **If you need to opt out** for a specific binding (e.g., binding to an ancestor or dynamically-set context), use `x:DataType=\"\"` locally to disable compilation for that element.\n\nWith `x:DataType` in place, any typo like `{Binding Themee}` will fail at compile time instead of silently failing at runtime.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"03671ab8-952b-45b9-8f59-8c6540938af4","outputTokens":535,"requestId":"E82F:29C906:25AB436:29B23CF:69F93E75"},"id":"5d54901f-1623-40b0-8776-9d1cc02c6afe","timestamp":"2026-05-05T00:49:05.077Z","parentId":"e5d683bf-3700-40df-b2df-5002246fd2ed"}
